Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eri? What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's going on, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, you still don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted Kouki-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did what I needed to do to get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in love with Kouki, you should\Nhave just confessed or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. That won't do at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-{\i1}kun {\i0}is too kind,\Nhe wouldn't make an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even surrounded by a trash heap of losers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's too nice,\Nhe couldn't leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make him\Ntruly mine and mine alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to go out of\Nmy way to take out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we landed in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking out the trash\Nis really hard in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, I can't allow anyone\Nto go back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-{\i1}kun {\i0}and I are going to live in\Nthis world together, for ever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others don't seem right, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Necromancy, of course!\NThey've been dead for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Necromancy doesn't\Nlet people talk and respond like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can thank my job,\NNecromancer, for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I modified regular necromancy so that some\Nmemories and thought patterns remain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing them to talk and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My own special necromancy spell...\NLet's call it "Spirit Binding."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to cast it right after death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can only cast it on one\Nperson at a time. What a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deaths won't go to waste!\NI'll put you all to good use!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Eri! If you do that, I won't--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't ever forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that,\Nsince you're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to Spirit Bind\Nyou properly so you'll be all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't see anyone else.\NYou'll always just look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will only speak words that I want\Nto hear. My own Kouki-{\i1}kun{\i0}, just for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm losing my mind just imagining it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eririn... Eri... You can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop!\N--Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Nakamura! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt? Are you sad?\NLet me hear a pretty scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to resist, curse me in your pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll still be my little puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pathetic little toy!\NBlessings to all deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridicule to every sorry soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Binding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more puppet, done and done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eri, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suzu. Thank you, for all you did\Nback in Japan and over here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were such a useful pawn when it\Ncame to letting me be near Kouki-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so bothersome, how everyone\Ntried to go along with the idea that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku and Kaori were the only ones\Nwho should be near Kouki-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no powers back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so entrapping them and destroying\Nthem would have taken too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I really have to\Nthank you for being you, Suzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so obviously clueless, I could\Ndo anything and let it come off as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:07:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being "Suzu Taniguchi's best friend"\Nwas so useful. So, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri! How could you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku, your expression is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've really truly despised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you get to play a special role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Role?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Kaori\Nwould react to being killed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by her best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You won't--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that hurt? Don't worry, I'm kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end this torment right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop, please! Eri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Shizuku. Pretending\Nto be your friend was truly revolting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Shackles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}, hold on! I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaori...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this sacred realm, the mother\Nof all existence gives her blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaze at the sky, those who desire.\NSee the light at the end of the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You just can't stop getting\Nin my way, can you?\N--That is the light of salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give prayer, show acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please snap out of it! Eri, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirasaki! Princess Liliana!\NAre you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyama-{\i1}san{\i0}?! Are you all right?\NWhat a terrible injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did! I finally got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You prefer me over Nagumo,\Ndon't you? Right, Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Mother...\NSmiling down from heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aetherflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up either,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Restrain him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamai! Sonobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamai! Don't cut my hand off, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mess up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu! A barrier! Protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in shock, it's only natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand your ground, Sakagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't hold them back,\NTamai and the others won't either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri! Hiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's close enough, Kouki-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki, why are you swinging\Nthat sword at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never taught you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meld-{\i1}san{\i0}, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meld-{\i1}san{\i0}... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Kouki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:13:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What is this? I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's finally working. That was\Nsupposed to be a pretty strong poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the prince wakes up\Nthe princess with a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the princess putting\Nthe prince to sleep with a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sounds like a good plot too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eri, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's not lethal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to kill you\Nwith my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a while, okay? Kouki-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Eri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Does it hurt? Are you sad?\N- Let me hear a pretty scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop!\N--Stop!\N--Does it hurt? Are you sad?\NLet me hear a pretty scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to resist, curse me in your pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop!\N--Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll still be my little puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop!\N--Eri!\N--A pathetic little toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:14:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blessings to all deaths!\NRidicule to every sorry soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tio, Sensei, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shirasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wheels of heaven shall not yet turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The vessel may be lost,\Nbut this soul is trapped in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's no use! She's already dead!\N--The vessel may be lost,\Nbut this soul is trapped in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's no use! She's already dead!\N--Then let us open a gate\Nto life in between worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, if you promise\Nnot to be hostile,\N--Then let us open a gate\Nto life in between worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can bring Kaori back to life using\Nmy magic. How does that sound?\N--ward off death,\Nand rebind the ties to this soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Wait, Nagumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these people around us.\NThey look alive, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything about the dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the least you could do\Nis keep them clean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you'd be able to do\Nas you please with Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, you definitely need me--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! You had your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Everyone, get down!\N--Oh no! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about your feelings or\Nyour motivations or whatever else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all you've got, then just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori would be mine... You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame others.\NYou're the only one to blame for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never take responsibility for\Nanything. You're a complete loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See if you can survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to attach her spirit, but it\Nwould take time to do anything further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like Yue's help if possible.\NThis won't last forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you value the life of your comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are one hundred thousand\Nmonsters outside the walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a million more coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how strong you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't continue fighting while\Nprotecting everything, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I say I'm friends\Nwith the kingdom or these others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to have a war,\Ngo right on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay out of my way. Otherwise,\NI'll vaporize you all, like I just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get my vengeance for this shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of my god, I will destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime, where's that ugly fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, where is that piece of trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}, Kaori... Kaori is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shea, take care of Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tio, guide Yue and the others.\NSensei, I need your help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Everyone, let's get to\Nthe top of the mountain. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai-{\i1}chan{\i0}-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of this!\NAi-{\i1}chan{\i0}-{\i1}sensei{\i0}, go help Kaori please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Sonobe-{\i1}san{\i0}, please take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaegashi, hold it together.\NJust believe in us and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise, you'll see Kaori again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay like this, who would\Nclean up after my messes from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:22:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can trust you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, "A New Journey."